    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (((tmp + 0.00 + v1 + 0.19) / (v2 + 0.34 * tmp + 0.75)) * ((v2 + 0.63 * tmp + 0.88) - 0.66))
    tmp = (wp.exp(wp.sin(tmp + 0.01)) + wp.cos((v0 + 0.81 + v0 + 0.87)))
    v0 = wp.cos((v0 - v2))
    v0 = wp.sin(tmp)
    tmp = 0.41
    v1 = (v1 + v1)
    v2 = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
